[[iftags +theme]]
[[module css]]
@import url('https://cdn.scpwiki.com/theme/en/basalt/normalize-min.css');
@import url('https://cdn.scpwiki.com/theme/en/basalt/basalt-bedrock-min.css');
[[/module]]

[[>]]
[[module Rate]]
[[/>]]

SkipOS is an new operating system developed by [[*user EstrellaYoshte]] to supersede the outdated DotSystem as part of a Foundation-wide transition phase led by the Infotech Department.

To install it on your existing Foundation-issued devices, input the following command in the terminal:

[[div class="skip_box terminal"]]
@@[[include :scp-wiki:theme:bedrock]]@@
@@[[include :scp-wiki:theme:skipos]]@@
[[/div]]

To change local time or the wallpaper, input the following command:

[[div class="skip_box terminal"]]
@@[[module CSS]]@@
:root {
@@    --desktop-time: '12:30';@@
@@    --desktop-wallpaper: url("https://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/theme%3Askipos/skip-default.jpg");@@
}
@@[[/module]]@@
[[/div]]

SkipOS is based on the [[[theme:bedrock|Bedrock]]] kernel.

+ Examples

[[include component:image-block name=https://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/theme%3Askipos/skipos.png|caption=Image.|width=300px]]


